    <title>python与linux命令差异</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/05/29/python%E4%B8%8Elinux%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/05/29/python与linux命令差异/</id>
    <published>2019-05-29T02:53:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-29T05:23:06.631Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>运维的小伙伴平时使用最多的就是linux命令，其中装个yum仓库自带的命令基本就够用。而python在linux中默认是已安装python2，需要导入对应的模块则可以实现相同的结果或去安装python3，先来介绍怎么下载安装git和hexo，以及如何在github上面关联。</p><h2 id="hexo-github搭建"><a href="#hexo-github搭建" class="headerlink" title="hexo+github搭建"></a>hexo+github搭建</h2><h3 id="git-amp-amp-hexo的安装"><a href="#git-amp-amp-hexo的安装" class="headerlink" title="git &amp;&amp; hexo的安装"></a>git &amp;&amp; hexo的安装</h3><p>1.首先要在windows机器上装上git以及hexo<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"你的GitHub用户名"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"你的GitHub注册邮箱"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>详细可以参考下面的链接进行git和hexo的下载：<br>More info:   <a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GIT|Download</a>       <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo|download</a></p><p>2.记得在你的github上面创建你的仓库，信任关系以及相关联的站点配置文件。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">仓库名: 用户名.github.io，类如我的就是：wnhho.github.io</span><br><span class="line">信任关系的建立:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$ssh</span>-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"你的GitHub注册邮箱"</span></span><br><span class="line">站点配置文件config的书写:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">repository: git@github.com:wnhho/wnhho.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">*记得每个冒号后面都有空格*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>详细可参考下面链接：<br>More info:   <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>   <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo|github搭建教程</a></p><p>3.最后清除缓存，生成文件以及上传gtihub<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$hexo</span> n <span class="string">"我的博客"</span> == hexo new <span class="string">"我的博客"</span> <span class="comment">#新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$hexo</span> g == hexo generate <span class="comment">#生成</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$hexo</span> s == hexo server <span class="comment">#启动服务预览</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$hexo</span> d == hexo deploy <span class="comment">#部署</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>推荐的搭建的3个文档和链接：</strong><br>More info : <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/201283bcd64a" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo|github基础</a>   <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/9f0e90cc32c2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">超酷炫网页效果</a>   <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42796909/article/details/81745271" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo博客书写规范</a></p><h3 id="Python与linux的差异"><a href="#Python与linux的差异" class="headerlink" title="Python与linux的差异"></a>Python与linux的差异</h3><h4 id="Python2与Python3的差异"><a href="#Python2与Python3的差异" class="headerlink" title="Python2与Python3的差异"></a>Python2与Python3的差异</h4><table><thead><tr><th>python2</th><th style="text-align:left">python3</th><th style="text-align:center">备注1</th><th style="text-align:right">备注2</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>print</td><td style="text-align:left">print()</td><td style="text-align:center">py2的print是一个语句</td><td style="text-align:right">py3的print是一个函数</td></tr><tr><td>&lt;&gt;和!=</td><td style="text-align:left">!=</td><td style="text-align:center">py2支持两中不等于</td><td style="text-align:right">py3支持一种</td></tr><tr><td>raw_input()和input()</td><td style="text-align:left">input</td><td style="text-align:center">py2有两个全局函数</td><td style="text-align:right">py3直接一个函数代替</td></tr><tr><td>[ i for i in 1, 2]</td><td style="text-align:left">[i for i in (1,2)]</td><td style="text-align:center">py2不需要加()</td><td style="text-align:right">p3则需要加()</td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>推荐python学习的网站</em><br>More info : <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/05810d38f93a?utm_campaign=maleskine&amp;utm_content=note&amp;utm_medium=seo_notes&amp;utm_source=recommendation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|django by example|</a>              <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/nobleman__/article/details/85730001" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|pycharm注册码|</a>         <a href="https://www.runoob.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|runoob|</a>             <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/c/00c61372c46a" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|python百例|</a>            <a href="https://www.python.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|python|</a></p><h4 id="Python与linux的语法区别"><a href="#Python与linux的语法区别" class="headerlink" title="Python与linux的语法区别"></a>Python与linux的语法区别</h4><p>1.查看当前的目录：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">pwd</span>  <span class="comment">#这个是linux环境下面绝对路径的命令</span></span><br><span class="line">$ import os <span class="comment"># python需要os模块</span></span><br><span class="line">$ cwd = os.getcwd()  相当于<span class="built_in">pwd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$print</span>(cwd) <span class="comment">#打印出当前的路径</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>*可以查看模仿每天主席生产备份的简单例子：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import tarfile</span><br><span class="line">import time</span><br><span class="line">import shutil</span><br><span class="line">dt = time.localtime()</span><br><span class="line">ft = <span class="string">"%Y%m%d"</span></span><br><span class="line">nt = time.strftime(ft,dt)</span><br><span class="line">path = <span class="string">'E:\小霸王\save'</span>+ <span class="string">'\\'</span> +  nt + <span class="string">'\\'</span> <span class="comment">#window环境'\'要使用'\\'代替奥</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(path)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#path = os.getcwd()</span></span><br><span class="line">name = nt + <span class="string">'_主席每日备份.tar.gz'</span></span><br><span class="line">def main():</span><br><span class="line">    tar = tarfile.open(name,<span class="string">'w:gz'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> root,dir,files <span class="keyword">in</span> os.walk(path):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> file <span class="keyword">in</span> files:</span><br><span class="line">            fullpath = os.path.join(root,file)</span><br><span class="line">            tar.add(fullpath)</span><br><span class="line">def move():</span><br><span class="line">    shutil.copy(name,<span class="string">'F:\\python安装目录\pycharm安装目录\python'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br><span class="line">    move()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2.表示当天的时间：<br>linux环境一般都是%Y%m%d 然后使用通配符*来表示匹配的<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ date = `date + %Y%m%d` <span class="comment">#linux一般这样表示年月日</span></span><br><span class="line">$ import time  <span class="comment">#python使用time这个模块</span></span><br><span class="line">$ date = time.strftime(%Y%m%d<span class="string">',time.localtime(time.time())) #其中%Y%m%d的排序可以自己定义这点我比较喜欢比较灵活</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>3.linux中的shell命令与python的shutil模块<br><em>基本python的shutil模块都可以是实习shell的命令，简单介绍如下：</em><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ cp file1 file2；rm -rf file1  <span class="comment">#linux下的复制和删除</span></span><br><span class="line">$ import shutil <span class="comment">#python中则使用shutil模块</span></span><br><span class="line">$ shutil.copy(name1,name2) ; shutil.move(name1,name2) <span class="comment">#使用该模块进行删除和拷贝</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>推荐python模块介绍和详细讲解链接：<br>More  info : <a href="https://yiyibooks.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">|yiyibooks|</a> </p>]]></content>
    
